 this in General Discussion.<br>
<br>
Clerics on a lot of other servers think that the effect of their BP has been nerfed.  Maybe it has, and VI has admitted to it.  They also say that this 'nerf' is a temporary one.  <br>
<br>
My suggestion would be to give the Cleric BP the effect Manaconvert (like the Manarobe and Cannibalize).<br>
<br>
That would be really cool I think. <p>Khirsa Maelstorm 55 Vicar<BR>
Legion of Heroes<BR>
<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uresomatic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Res O Matic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 154<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/15/01 2:39:39 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://images.honesty.com/imagedata/h/970/24/29702410.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: New Cleric BP effect</span><hr size=1> Looks like they opted to put Mark of Karn on the breastplate.  I haven't talked to my cleric friends yet, but depending on how much they improved it, this might actually be a nice change.  9 second cast time as well, which makes it combat useable <p><CENTER><img src="http://images.honesty.com/imagedata/h/002/82/30028236.jpg"> </CENTER>
</P>
